夢が KIRA-KIRA
Dreams are KIRA-KIRA

73
00:07:34,548 --> 00:07:35,848
無駄に KIRA-KIRA？
Uselessly KIRA-KIRA?

74
00:07:35,848 --> 00:07:37,048
前進だ DOKA-DOKA!
Move forward, DOKA-DOKA!

75
00:07:37,048 --> 00:07:38,248
はわっ 通りまる
Hawa! Passing through

76
00:07:38,248 --> 00:07:39,248
キマッちゃってる！
We're on a roll!

77
00:07:39,248 --> 00:07:40,548
全速モードでよいしょっしょ
In full speed mode, let's go, let's go

78
00:07:40,548 --> 00:07:41,848
制限はね無視だよ
Ignore the limits, you know

79
00:07:41,848 --> 00:07:43,048
なんでもかんでもやっぱっぱ
Anything and everything, you know

80
00:07:43,048 --> 00:07:44,248
全力がいいよね
Full power is the best, right?

81
00:07:44,248 --> 00:07:45,348
笑顔あり
