ニューレコードの更新は続くんだってば
The updating of new records will continue, I'm telling you

125
00:09:10,548 --> 00:09:12,848
地球からやってきたボクらよ
We who came from Earth

126
00:09:12,848 --> 00:09:14,848
やりまくれ Go ahead! Go ahead!
Do it all, Go ahead! Go ahead!

127
00:09:14,848 --> 00:09:17,548
さあ次の星へ！
Now, to the next star!

128
00:09:22,548 --> 00:09:24,348
一歩が百歩の始まり
One step is the beginning of a hundred

129
00:09:24,348 --> 00:09:27,248
だから行こうよすぐに行こうよ
So let's go, let's go right now

130
00:09:27,248 --> 00:09:29,848
無理は道理よりも強引だなー
Pushing too hard is more forceful than reason

131
00:09:30,148 --> 00:09:32,548
瞬間をキミと一緒にね
That moment, together with you

132
00:09:32,548 --> 00:09:33,248
MONSTER!

133
00:09:33,248 --> 00:09:36,148
真っ暗な空かもしれないけどボクらは負けない
It might be a pitch-black sky, but we won't lose

134
00:09:36,148 --> 00:09:38,248
お目々を開いてお目々を離すなよー
Open your eyes, don't look away!

135
00:09:38,248 --> 00:09:39,848
MONSTER! HEY! MONSTER! HEY! MONSTER!

136
00:09:39,848 --> 00:09:44,848
前人未到の宇宙に全速の全力で Goだ Yeah!!
Into the unexplored universe, at full speed and full power, let's go, Yeah!!

137
00:10:00,023 --> 00:10:01,223
全開かい そうだそうだっ
Are you at full throttle? Yes, that's right!

138
00:10:01,323 --> 00:10:02,823
地球はブルーだブルーだっ
The Earth is blue, so blue!

139
00:10:03,023 --> 00:10:08,023
ぜんぶを欲しがれ EARTH女子!
Want it all, Earth Girls!

140
00:10:08,523 --> 00:10:10,023
全開かい そうかもそうかもっ
Are you at full throttle? Maybe, just maybe!

141
00:10:10,123 --> 00:10:13,223
宇宙のスターにスターにっ
To be a star, a star in the universe!

142
00:10:13,523 --> 00:10:15,523
なりたい! なりたい!
I want to be! I want to be!

143
00:10:15,823 --> 00:10:18,523
なれそう? なれそうだよう!
Can I be? It looks like I can!

144
00:10:23,023 --> 00:10:23,723
キマっちゃったしね!
We've decided on it!

145
00:10:23,823 --> 00:10:25,723
全速モードでよいしょっしょ 制限はね 無視だよ
Yoishossho at full speed mode, limitations are ignored!

146
00:10:25,823 --> 00:10:28,423
なんでもかんでもやっぱっぱ 全力がいいよね
Whatever it is, doing our best is the best!

147
00:10:28,523 --> 00:10:30,823
メガ回れ ヒメガ回れ
Spin around mega, spin around hime-mega

148
00:10:30,923 --> 00:10:32,623
最強 BIG BANG 狙っちゃえ未来!
Aim for the future with the strongest BIG BANG!

149
00:10:32,723 --> 00:10:33,723
チェストー!
Chest!

150
00:10:33,823 --> 00:10:36,123
手とりあったるんたった 怖くはないよね
Holding hands, run-tatta, it's not scary, is it?

151
00:10:36,223 --> 00:10:38,723
夢の計測メーターは 振り切れそうだよ
The dream measurement meter is about to fly off!

152
00:10:38,823 --> 00:10:40,823
地球から やってきたボクラは
We, who came from Earth,

153
00:10:40,923 --> 00:10:42,823
本日も Go ahead! Go ahead!
Are still going ahead today! Go ahead!

154
00:10:42,923 --> 00:10:44,223
怒られるまで…
Until we get scolded...

155
00:10:44,323 --> 00:10:47,423
…怒られても止まらないのです
...even if we get scolded, we won't stop!

156
00:10:47,523 --> 00:10:49,023
最後の最後もごめんなさーい!
So sorry, even at the very end!

157
00:10:49,123 --> 00:10:50,823
先鋒だれだい? ボクらだい!
Who's the vanguard? We are!

158
00:10:50,923 --> 00:10:53,223
